{"lemma":"فَعْلَة","slug":"فَعْلَة","root":"ف.ع.ل","root_slug":"ف-ع-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ع-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34194","n34200","n34201","n34202"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deed; act; action"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of فَاعِل (fāʕil)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from فَعَلَ (faʕala, “to do”).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":["/faʕ.la/","/fa.ʕa.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34194","headword_ar":"فَعَلَهُ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K, *) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolN","text_ar":"فَعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEaAlN","text_ar":"فَعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst. therefrom, (S, O, Msb, K, *) but, accord. to Ibn-Kemál, it has become commonly used as the inf. n.; MF, however, says that its being thus used requires consideration; and it is said that there is no instance like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalahu","text_ar":"فَعَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoEaluhu","text_ar":"يَفْعَلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHarahu","text_ar":"سَحَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yasoHaruhu","text_ar":"يَسْحَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siHorN","text_ar":"سِحْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or, to these may be added as sometimes occurring,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadaEa","text_ar":"خَدَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxodaEu","text_ar":"يَخْدَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadoEN","text_ar":"خَدْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xidoEN","text_ar":"خِدْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaraEa","text_ar":"صَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSoraEu","text_ar":"يَصْرَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaroEN","text_ar":"صَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiroEN","text_ar":"صِرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; namely, a thing (S, O. [For further explanation see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]) [In the Kur. xxi. 73,] some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^awoHayonaA A_ilayohimo faEola","text_ar":"وَاَوْحَيْنَا اـِلَيْهِمْ فَعْلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@loxayoraAti","text_ar":"ا@لْخَيْرَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And we suggested to them the doing of good works"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Lth, S, O;) others reading ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEola","text_ar":"فِعْلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxyrAt","text_ar":"الخيرات"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, O.) ―         -b2-  And one says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala bihi","text_ar":"فَعَلَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"something]. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala A@ll~`hu bihi","text_ar":"فَعَلَ ا@للّٰهُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a form of imprecation, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God do to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"what He will do; i. e. may God punish him: see an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZolamu","text_ar":"اَظْلَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEala biAlmaroA^api","text_ar":"فَعَلَ بِالمَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"often occurs in trads. &c. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He compressed the woman."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n34200","headword_ar":"فَعْلَةٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEol","text_ar":"فِعْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Msb, TA,) with fet-h. (Msb.) Thus in the saying in the Kur [xxvi. 18],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafaEalota faEolataka A@A~atiY faEalota","text_ar":"وَفَعَلْتَ فَعْلَتَكَ ا@اَّتِى فَعَلْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And thou hast done thy one deed that thou hast done"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as though the speaker said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatalota Aln~afosa","text_ar":"فَتَلْتَ النَّفْسَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatollataka","text_ar":"قَتْللَتَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in which Esh-Shaabee read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolataka","text_ar":"فِعْلَتَكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy kind of deed"},{"kind":"text","text":"], with kesr, as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatalota Alqitolapa","text_ar":"فَتَلْتَ القِتْلَةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al~atiY qado EarafotahaA","text_ar":"الَّتِى قَدْ عَرَفْتَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says Zj; but he adds that the former reading is better. (TA.) And [hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAnato minohu faEolapN HasanapN","text_ar":"كَانَتْ مِنْهُ فَعْلَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabiyHapN","text_ar":"قَبِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good single deed proceeded from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"one]. (S, O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n34201","headword_ar":"فِعْلَةٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n34202","headword_ar":"فَعِلَةٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A custom, manner, habit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wont."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}